    "To avoid this issue, ACLF slows down its data transmission rate.",
    "That's why overall throughput is lower, and this issue is depicted in Fig. 9.",
    "In BSN-Care architecture, they implement their model using a single server.",
    "This server is used to save all kinds of records.",
    "That's why there are network congestion issues during transmission."
